tags.description:
`example-haxcms-theme`

Attributes:

  * `edit-mode` {`boolean`} - Edit mode which will be updated whenever HAXcms store
has been updated. It's also reflected to attribute which
is a Polymer convention to allow it to be leveraged in
CSS styling.

  * `active-manifest-index` {`number`} - Current array index of the active page that's been loaded.
